companyName: iShares MSCI Hong Kong Index Fund
description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the MSCI Hong Kong Index.
 The fund will at all times invest at least 80% of its assets in the securities of its underlying index and in depositary receipts representing securities in its underlying index. The underlying index consists of stocks traded primarily on the Stock Exchange of Hong Kong Limited (SEHK). It may include large-, mid- or small-capitalization companies. The fund is non-diversified.
